PetroSA Hasn't Applied For Karoo, Waterberg Permits, Business Report Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-09T05:29:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/petrosa-hasn-t-applied-for-karoo-waterberg-permits-business-report-says.html
PetroSA,  South Africa ’s state-owned
oil and gas company, hasn’t applied for technical co-operation
permits to explore the potential of gas “fracking” in the
Karoo region or for cobalt methane in the Waterberg area of the
Limpopo province, Business Report said, citing Chief Financial
Officer Nkosemntu Nika.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  